-- EU to Allow Air Strikes Into Somali Territory, Spiegel Reports
-- B y   C o r n e l i u s   R a h n
-- 2012-03-26T14:52:09Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-26/eu-to-allow-air-strikes-into-somali-territory-spiegel-reports.html
European Union foreign ministers
agreed to extend the Atalanta anti-piracy mission to allow air
strikes up to 2 kilometers (1.2 miles) into Somali territory,
 Der Spiegel  reported, without saying how it got the information.  To contact the reporter on this story:
